\newlabel{fig:rewardfig}{{10}{21}{Reward-ablation figures for the revised bundle in both universes. Reward choice moves the legacy controller within a narrow band, but does not change the broader ranking versus the factor core and the strongest robust controllers}{figure.caption.25}{}}
